Episode 1
 
Keith Lemon is back with a third series of Through the Keyhole. Join Keith as he rummages around three mystery celebrity houses unearthing clues for the studio panel to guess 'who habitates in a house like this.' On this week's star-studded panel are celebrity chef Gino D'Acampo, Corrie battle-axe Sue Cleaver and comedian Johnny Vegas.
